{"data":[{"date":"06:28 14/08","title":"T\u00e2n binh Inter ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 th\u1eddi th\u01a1 \u1ea5u","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/14/tan-binh-inter-hoan-tat-giac-mo-thoi-tho-au.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Inter Milan ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Keita Balde d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n t\u1eeb Monaco. Trong ng\u00e0y ra m\u1eaft, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 th\u1eddi th\u01a1 \u1ea5u \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Nerazzurri.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Keita r\u1eddi Lazio \u0111\u1ebfn Monaco</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKeita Balde Diao l\u00e0 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t kh\u00f4ng xa l\u1ea1 g\u00ec v\u1edbi c\u00e1c C\u0110V Inter Milan. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995 t\u1eebng c\u00f3 4 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Lazio ch\u01a1i t\u1ea1i Serie A. Th\u00e1ng 8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, anh chuy\u1ec3n sang ch\u01a1i cho Monaco t\u1ea1i Ligue 1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a cu\u1ed9c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00e0y t\u1edbi t\u1eeb s\u1ef1 b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed3ng gi\u1eefa Lazio v\u00e0 Keita. Sang Monaco, anh th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi 8 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng sau 23 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n t\u1ea1i Ligue 1. Th\u00f4ng qua \u0111\u00f3, Keita nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1eeb CLB trong m\u01a1, Inter Milan.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Inter Milan ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Keita Balde h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Inter Milan ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Keita Balde h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/14/Keita-gia-nhap-Inter.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Inter Milan ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Keita Balde</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Gia nh\u1eadp Inter</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nInter Milan ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Keita Balde d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n t\u1eeb Monaco. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat n\u00e0y s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i cho Nerazzurri d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n 1 n\u0103m v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c ph\u00eda 6 tri\u1ec7u Euro. Inter c\u0169ng c\u00e0i v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n mua \u0111\u1ee9t tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Senegal v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 30 tri\u1ec7u Euro v\u00e0o n\u0103m sau.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nPh\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u trong ng\u00e0y ra m\u1eaft, Keita th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ebfn Inter l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 th\u00e0nh hi\u1ec7n th\u1ef1c. \u201cT\u00f4i r\u1ea5t vui khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y v\u00e0 s\u1ebd c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac\u201d, anh n\u00f3i tr\u00ean k\u00eanh truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Inter.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Italia v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t kh\u00e1t v\u1ecdng l\u1edbn khi kho\u00e1c \u00e1o m\u1ed9t CLB l\u1edbn. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m \u1edf Serie A v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t. Khi c\u00f2n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ee9a tr\u1ebb, t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n m\u01a1 \u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i cho Inter v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. T\u00f4i lu\u00f4n y\u00eau th\u00edch c\u00e1c C\u0110V c\u1ee7a Inter. H\u1ecd lu\u00f4n t\u1eed t\u1ebf v\u00e0 l\u1ecbch s\u1ef1. \u1ede th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, t\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 mang t\u1edbi ni\u1ec1m vui cho h\u1ecd m\u1ed7i tu\u1ea7n.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n1h30 r\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng th\u1ee9 2 t\u1edbi (20/8), Inter s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi. H\u1ecd l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Sassuolo t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1 Serie A 2018/19.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Serie A tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/ac-milan-chi-110-trieu-euro-mua-milinkovicsavic-176-194386.html\">C\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng chi 110 tri\u1ec7u euro mua Pogba Serbia</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/hlv-massimiliano-allegri-phat-bieu-ve-cristiano-ronaldo-176-194396.html\">Ronaldo ghi b\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, HLV Juventus n\u1ed5 vang</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/ronaldo-muon-juventus-mua-muc-tieu-so-1-cua-mu-o-he-2018-176-194317.html\">Ronaldo mu\u1ed1n Juventus mua m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a MU</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/ronaldo-thuc-giuc-nguoi-ban-than-marcelo-den-juventus-176-194109.html\">Ronaldo th\u00fac gi\u1ee5c ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea1n th\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn Juventus</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/co-cristiano-ronaldo-serie-a-doi-logo-176-194058.html\">C\u00f3 Cristiano Ronaldo, Serie A CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C \u0111\u1ed5i sang logo m\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5453","checkdouble":"194422"},{"date":"18:08 13/08","title":"C\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 t\u1ea1i ASIAD c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam m\u1ea1nh y\u1ebfu th\u1ebf n\u00e0o?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/13/cac-doi-thu-tai-asiad-cua-dt-olympic-viet-nam-manh-yeu-the-nao.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>V\u00e0o chi\u1ec1u mai 14/8, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018. V\u00e0 h\u00e3y c\u00f9ng Bongda24h \u0111i\u1ec3m qua c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i.\r\n\r\n\r\n</h2><br>\r\n<h2>Olympic Pakistan</h2>\r\n<h2><o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 \u0110T Pakistan \u0111ang x\u1ebfp cu\u1ed1i tr\u00ean BXH b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi sau 3 n\u0103m ch\u1ecbu l\u1ec7nh c\u1ea5m thi \u0111\u1ea5u qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf c\u1ee7a FIFA, tuy nhi\u00ean kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i v\u00ec v\u1eady m\u00e0 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p xem nh\u1eb9 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Olympic c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam \u00c1 s\u1edf h\u1eefu nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u00e0 h\u1ecd h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo. Tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, \u0111\u1ed9i Olympic Pakistan c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t n\u1eeda s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi t\u1edbi Indonesia, Olympic Pakistan v\u1eeba t\u1eadp hu\u1ea5n d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n \u1edf Bahrain v\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 1 th\u1eafng, 2 h\u00f2a v\u00e0 1 thua trong 4 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf Qatar.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"C\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 t\u1ea1i ASIAD c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam m\u1ea1nh y\u1ebfu th\u1ebf n\u00e0o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"C\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 t\u1ea1i ASIAD c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam m\u1ea1nh y\u1ebfu th\u1ebf n\u00e0o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/Cac-doi-thu-tai-ASIAD-cua-DT-Olympic-Viet-Nam-manh-yeu-the-nao-hinh-anh.jpeg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em><span style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-align: justify;\">Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n g\u1eb7p&nbsp;</span>\u0110T Olympic Pakistan</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, Olympic Pakistan c\u00f3 7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea7y 20 tu\u1ed5i. Gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, HLV Jose Antonio Nogueira c\u1ee7a Olympic Pakistan c\u0169ng tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp ba g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean 23 tu\u1ed5i g\u1ed3m th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Yousuf Butt ( sinh ra t\u1ea1i Canada) v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Saddam Hussain. &nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hussain hi\u1ec7n ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng cho Larnaka Gencler Birligi S.K, CLB c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ea3o S\u00edp. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i (c\u00f9ng Yousuf Butt) trong l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng 20 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Olympic Pakistan. T\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 25 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u 19 tr\u1eadn cho \u0110T Pakistan.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p c\u00f3 t\u01b0 t\u01b0\u1edfng ch\u1ee7 quan l\u01a1 l\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y. Tr\u1eadn Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Pakistan c\u0169ng l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1edbm nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3ng D di\u1ec5n ra l\u00fac 16h00 ng\u00e0y 14/8. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 n\u1eafm t\u1edbi 90% c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng knock-out c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>Olympic Nepal <o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">So v\u1edbi Pakistan, Olympic Nepal t\u1edbi t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t n\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u00edt t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i h\u01a1n. H\u1ecd c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1eb7t n\u1eb7ng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y. V\u1edbi th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n g\u1ed3m nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb, Olympic Nepal c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng &lsquo;\u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00e2n, \u0111\u1ed3ng l\u1ea1ng&rsquo; v\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">G\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1edbi t\u1eeb Nam \u00c1 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Bimal Gharti Magar. Anh l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb th\u1ee9 6 tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi ra m\u1eaft \u0110TQG khi m\u1edbi 14 tu\u1ed5i. M\u1ed9t n\u0103m sau \u0111\u00f3, Magar \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean cho \u0110T Nepal. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ed9t c\u00e1i t\u00ean kh\u00e1c c\u0169ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng l\u00e0 Ananta Tamang. H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 v\u1eeba tr\u00f2n 20 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u 14 tr\u1eadn cho \u0110T Nepal. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f9ng U23 Nepal gi\u00e0nh HCV c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ed9i Th\u1ec3 thao Nam \u00c1 hai n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc. V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n, Ananta Tamang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u00ec v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Nepal c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ed9i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1ea1i Indonesia.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Olympic Nepal\" title=\"Olympic Nepal\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/football.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Olympic Nepal kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ngang t\u1ea7m v\u1edbi \u0110T&nbsp;<span style=\"text-align: justify;\">Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a&nbsp;th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Koji Gyotoku t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018 ch\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu l\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ecd x\u00e1t, t\u00edch l\u0169y kinh nghi\u1ec7m \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u mang t\u1ea7m ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c, qua \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00fap c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb c\u00f3 th\u00eam kinh nghi\u1ec7m chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ed9i Th\u1ec3 thao Nam \u00c1 \u1edf Bangladesh v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 3/2019.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m ASIAD 2018, Olympic Nepal v\u1eeba c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn thua tan t\u00e1c 0-4 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t trong th\u1eddi gian qua l\u00e0 Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan. C\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 4 n\u0103m, Nepal c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec3 thua tr\u1eafng c\u1ea3 3 tr\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iraq, Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u00e0 Kuwait v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 13 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 n\u1ed5i m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0o t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2014. Nh\u1eefng d\u1eef li\u1ec7u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/lich-thi-dau-va-ket-qua-bong-da-nam-asiad-2018-472-193926.html\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asiad 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/lich-thi-dau-u23-viet-nam-ket-qua-tai-asiad-2018-472-193923.html\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i Asiad 2018</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u00e0 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 nguy hi\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5t m\u00e0 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u1edbi l\u1ee9a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed9i U21.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng mang sang Indonesia \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao t\u1eebng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u \u1ea5n \u1edf c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i tr\u1ebb nh\u01b0 Takumi Minamino, Ritsu Doan hay Takefusa Kubo nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1eebng gi\u00e0nh HCV ASIAD 2010 v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 tr\u00ean c\u01a1 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nh\u1eadt c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb kh\u00e1 nghi\u00eam t\u00fac cho gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u khi t\u1eebng sang Ph\u00e1p tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf v\u00e0 thu v\u1ec1 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng khi th\u1eafng. U21 Nh\u1eadt khi \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i U21 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 3-2&nbsp;v\u00e0 c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a \u0111\u1ed9i U23 Canada v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 1-1.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Olympic Nhat Ban\" title=\"Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/aflo-jyfa073725.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n kh\u00f4ng mang \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn 'tr\u00ean c\u01a1' \u0110T&nbsp;<span style=\"text-align: justify;\">Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span></em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u1ea7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y. V\u1edbi nguy c\u01a1 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea1m m\u1eb7t Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c ngay \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo c\u1ea7n gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nh\u1eadt \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1eafc su\u1ea5t nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ec3 h\u00f2a ho\u1eb7c thua, h\u1ecd ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3i r\u01a1i v\u00e0o th\u1ebf kh\u00f3 \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean 100% quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m v\u00e0 s\u1ee9c l\u1ef1c m\u00e0 h\u1ecd c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n t\u1ec9nh t\u00e1o, b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh tr\u00e1nh r\u01a1i v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i b\u1eaby c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/chuyen-gia-viet-canh-bao-thay-tro-park-hang-seo-truoc-tran-gap-pakistan-168-194390.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/chuyen-gia-viet-canh-bao-thay-tro-park-hang-seo-truoc-tran-gap-pakistan.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/chuyen-gia-viet-canh-bao-thay-tro-park-hang-seo-truoc-tran-gap-pakistan-168-194390.html\">Chuy\u00ean gia Vi\u1ec7t c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Pakistan</span><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 Olympic Pakistan v\u00e0o chi\u1ec1u mai, c\u1ef1u HLV Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u00e0nh Vinh \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng cho r\u1eb1ng th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Park Hang Seo kh\u00f4ng...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thu-quan-olympic-pakistan-len-tieng-truoc-tran-gap-olympic-viet-nam-168-194384.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/1/Cac-doi-thu-tai-ASIAD-cua-DT-Olympic-Viet-Nam-manh-yeu-the-nao-hinh-anh.jpeg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thu-quan-olympic-pakistan-len-tieng-truoc-tran-gap-olympic-viet-nam-168-194384.html\">Th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n Olympic Pakistan l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi, ng\u01b0\u1eddi gi\u1eef b\u0103ng th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n Olympic Pakistan Saddam Hussain \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng khi \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u00ecnh s\u1eafp \u0111\u1ed1i  m\u1eb7t, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;&#xA;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5452","checkdouble":"194404"},{"date":"19:17 13/08","title":"HLV Park Hang Seo nghi \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam b\u1ecb n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/13/hlv-park-hang-seo-nghi-dt-olympic-viet-nam-bi-nuoc-chu-nha-choi-xau.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi chi\u1ec1u 13/8, v\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 nghi ng\u1edd vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 b\u1ecb Indonesia c\u1ed1 t\u00ecnh ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u.</h2><br>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Bu\u1ed5i chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y 13/8, bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 di\u1ec5n ra nh\u01b0 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch do m\u1eb7t s\u00e2n c\u1ecf t\u1ea1i khu c\u00f4ng nghi\u1ec7p Samsung qu\u00e1 x\u1ea5u, kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n, d\u1ec5 g\u00e2y ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y bu\u1ed9c th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo ph\u1ea3i di chuy\u1ec3n sang s\u00e2n c\u1ecf nh\u00e2n t\u1ea1o d\u00e0nh cho 7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ngay b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Park Hang Seo t\u1ed1 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam b\u1ecb n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Park Hang Seo t\u1ed1 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam b\u1ecb n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/38949054_1874678475957763_2958757035539169280_n.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Park Hang Seo kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 c\u00e1ch t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb sau bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp, HLV Park Hang Seo t\u1ecf ra c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 t\u1ee9c gi\u1eadn v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1eeb ph\u00eda n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0. V\u1ecb HLV 59 tu\u1ed5i n\u00f3i: &ldquo;T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o, nh\u01b0ng r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng ph\u00eda Indonsesia c\u00f3 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 t\u1eeb kh\u00e2u b\u1ed1c th\u0103m t\u1edbi b\u00e2y gi\u1edd. S\u00e2n t\u1eadp ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng k\u00e9m v\u00e0 b\u1ea5t h\u1ee3p l\u00fd. V\u00ec th\u1ebf, kh\u00e2u chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia r\u1ea5t thi\u1ebfu&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o, nh\u01b0ng r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng ph\u00eda Indonsesia c\u00f3 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 t\u1eeb kh\u00e2u b\u1ed1c th\u0103m t\u1edbi b\u00e2y gi\u1edd. S\u00e2n t\u1eadp ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng k\u00e9m v\u00e0 b\u1ea5t h\u1ee3p l\u00fd. V\u00ec th\u1ebf, kh\u00e2u chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia r\u1ea5t thi\u1ebfu&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng nhi\u1ec1u t\u1edbi quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam nh\u01b0 l\u1eddi \u00f4ng Park kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh: Tinh th\u1ea7n, \u00fd ch\u00ed quy\u1ebft th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t, v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. V\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i, m\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n mang l\u1ea1i cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ef1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i hi\u1ec3u r\u1eb1ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n mang l\u1ea1i ni\u1ec1m vui cho Vi\u1ec7t Nam&rdquo;.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/lich-thi-dau-u23-viet-nam-ket-qua-tai-asiad-2018-472-193923.html\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i Asiad 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/lich-thi-dau-va-ket-qua-bong-da-nam-asiad-2018-472-193926.html\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asiad 2018</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n ng\u00e0y mai g\u1eb7p Pakistan, HLV Park Hang Seo cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;Theo t\u00f4i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft th\u00ec Pakistan c\u00f3 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean 23 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0110an M\u1ea1ch. D\u00f9 v\u1eady t\u00f4i c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t \u00edt th\u00f4ng tin v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u1eafm b\u0103ng h\u00ecnh c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Pakistan v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Bahrain. H\u1ecd ch\u01a1i v\u1edbi s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 4-4-2 r\u1ea5t ch\u1eb7t ch\u1ebd. H\u1ecd s\u1ebd thi \u0111\u1ea5u quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eb9&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Park Hang Seo cho bi\u1ebft tinh th\u1ea7n, s\u1ee9c kho\u1ebb c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 r\u1ea5t h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n.Thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 \u00f4ng s\u1ebd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt 3-4-3 \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Pakistan.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 Olympic Pakistan s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra l\u00fac 16h ng\u00e0y mai tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Wibawa Mukti (Cikarang). Bongda24h s\u1ebd t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u n\u00e0y, mong b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ecdc ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u00f3n xem.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/cac-doi-thu-tai-asiad-cua-dt-olympic-viet-nam-manh-yeu-the-nao-168-194404.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/13/cac-doi-thu-tai-asiad-cua-dt-olympic-viet-nam-manh-yeu-the-nao.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/cac-doi-thu-tai-asiad-cua-dt-olympic-viet-nam-manh-yeu-the-nao-168-194404.html\">C\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 t\u1ea1i ASIAD c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam m\u1ea1nh y\u1ebfu th\u1ebf n\u00e0o?</span><br>\r\nV\u00e0o chi\u1ec1u mai 14/8, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018. V\u00e0 h\u00e3y c\u00f9ng Bongda24h \u0111i\u1ec3m qua c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i tham d\u1ef1...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5451","checkdouble":"194410"},{"date":"21:43 13/08","title":"Bayern Munich nh\u1eadn tin c\u1ef1c vui t\u1eeb tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0110\u1ee9c","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/13/bayern-munich-nhan-tin-cuc-vui-tu-tru-cot.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>David Alaba ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1edf d\u00e2y ch\u1eb1ng, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn t\u1eeb ph\u00eda HLV Niko Kovac.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">David Alaba d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBayern Munich \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n Eintracht Frankfurt trong tr\u1eadn Si\u00eau c\u00fap n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c, v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i c\u00f9ng quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m r\u1ea5t cao, \u201cH\u00f9m x\u00e1m\u201d \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 5-0.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"David Alaba ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, HLV Niko Kovac l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"David Alaba ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, HLV Niko Kovac l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/David-Alaba-chan-thuong,-HLV-Niko-Kovac-len-tieng-hinh-anh.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Alaba d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc\u00a0Eintracht Frankfurt</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Robert Lewandowski \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u00fa hat-trick. Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc\u00a0 Eintracht Frankfurt gi\u00fap \u201cH\u00f9m x\u00e1m\u201d h\u01b0ng ph\u1ea5n b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 c\u1ef1c \u0111\u1eaft.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 David Alaba ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Eintracht Frankfurt, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00c1o g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 sau pha va ch\u1ea1m m\u1ea1nh v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n cho r\u1eb1ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ee9t d\u00e2y ch\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0i th\u00e1ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Bayern n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Alaba</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00c1o, HLV Niko Kovac \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng. David Alaba ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1edf d\u00e2y ch\u1eb1ng, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn t\u1eeb ph\u00eda t\u00e2n HLV c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alba\" title=\"Alba\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/bayern-munich-nhan-tin-cuc-vui-tu-tru-cot.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Alaba kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ee9t d\u00e2y ch\u1eb1ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\"Alaba g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Eintracht Frankfurt, \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y b\u1ecb t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. Alaba \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c ki\u1ec3m tra, \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 y t\u1ebf k\u1ebft lu\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng d\u00e2y ch\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cHi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i t\u00f4i v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 k\u1ebft lu\u1eadn c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u bao nhi\u00eau l\u00e2u, Alaba v\u1eabn c\u1ea7n th\u00eam nh\u1eefng bu\u1ed5i ki\u1ec3m tra \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u1ebft lu\u1eadn v\u1ec1 m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBayern Munich s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 danh hi\u1ec7u Bundesliga v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 24 th\u00e1ng 8, \u1edf tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n Bundesliga 2018/19 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Hoffenheim.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5450","checkdouble":"194414"},{"date":"19:18 13/08","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 13/08: Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C r\u1eddi MU","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/13/diem-tin-bong-da-24h-toi-ngay-1308-them-mot-cau-thu-chinh-thuc-roi-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 13/08.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 r\u1eddi MU</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 1308 James Wilson r\u1eddi MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 1308 James Wilson r\u1eddi MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/wilson.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Wilson ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c r\u1eddi MU</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nMan United \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o James Wilson t\u1edbi CLB Aberdeen \u0111\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Real l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch cu\u1ed7m m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Barca</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Adrien Rabiot c\u1ee7a PSG. \u0110\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia v\u00f4 t\u00ecnh l\u00e0m \u0111au l\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea1i k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch Barcelona, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi theo \u0111u\u1ed5i ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p trong th\u1eddi gian kh\u00e1 l\u00e2u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Pep c\u00f3 v\u00e0i \u0111i\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ebfn Man City v\u00e0 Sterling</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Man City gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Raheem Sterling, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a HLV Pep Guardiola. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi TBN mu\u1ed1n BL\u0110 Man xanh nhanh ch\u00f3ng k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/pep-co-vai-dieu-muon-gui-den-man-city-va-sterling-172-194403.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/15/pep-co-vai-dieu-muon-gui-den-man-city-va-sterling.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/pep-co-vai-dieu-muon-gui-den-man-city-va-sterling-172-194403.html\">Pep c\u00f3 v\u00e0i \u0111i\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ebfn Man City v\u00e0 Sterling</span><br>\r\nMan City gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Raheem Sterling, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a HLV Pep Guardiola. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi TBN mu\u1ed1n BL\u0110 Man xanh nhanh ch\u00f3ng k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Real mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 th\u00eam 2 t\u00e2n binh \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lopetegui cua Real\" title=\"Lopetegui cua Real\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/30/Lopetegui-cua-Real.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Lopetegui mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 th\u00eam 2 t\u00e2n binh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Julen Lopetegui mu\u1ed1n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid mua th\u00eam 2 t\u00e2n binh trong th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Real v\u00e0 Barca nh\u1eadn tin vui v\u1ee5 sao kh\u1ee7ng PSG</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Adriano Rabiot r\u1eddi PSG \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra \u0111i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>C\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng chi 110 tri\u1ec7u euro mua &quot;Pogba Serbia&quot;</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">AC Milan r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n mua Sergej Milinkovic-Savic c\u1ee7a Lazio, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 110 tri\u1ec7u euro mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Monaco s\u1eafp c\u00f3 Nzonzi</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Ph\u00e1p, Monaco s\u1eafp chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Nzonzi t\u1eeb Sevilla, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Arsenal v\u00e0&nbsp;Monaco \u1edf H\u00e8 n\u00e0y. \u0110\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 30 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng C\u00f4ng qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf ra 32 tri\u1ec7u euro.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>MU s\u1eafp gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Mata v\u00e0 Herrera</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"MU len ke hoach giu chan Mata va Herrera\" title=\"MU l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Mata v\u00e0 Herrera\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/herrrera-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Mata v\u00e0 Herrera</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Mirror, M.U \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u00eam 2 n\u0103m v\u1edbi b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha, Juan Mata v\u00e0 Ander Herrera. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i n\u00e0y v\u1edbi Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ebfn H\u00e8 2019.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Barca n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i mua Pogba</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Barca kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Paul Pogba, song h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng chi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5449","checkdouble":"194411"},{"date":"23:25 13/08","title":"3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Anh mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 \"th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng\" c\u1ee7a Real Madrid","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/13/3-doi-bong-anh-muon-co-than-dong-cua-real-madrid.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Anh bao g\u1ed3m Middlebrough, Aston Villa v\u00e0 Derby County mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Martin Odegaard r\u1eddi Real Madrid \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Martin Odegaard kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng \u1edf Real</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMartin Odegaard \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 c\u1ef1c cao, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1998 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 \u201cth\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng\u201d c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Na Uy, anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean tri\u1ec3n v\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Odegaard bat ngo duoc dang ky da Champions League\" title=\"Odegaard b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd \u0111\u00e1 Champions League\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2016/9/4/Nghi-van-Zidane-lai-bi-ep-dung-Odegaard-o-Champions-League-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Odegaard kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng \u1edf Real Madrid</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Na Uy gia nh\u1eadp Real Madrid t\u1eeb Stromsgodset v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1/2015. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 19 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh v\u00e0 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai g\u1ea7n.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, khi c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Bernabeu Odegaard l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, anh ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n c\u00f3 1 l\u1ea7n trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i 1 c\u1ee7a Los Blancos. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1998 ra \u0111i theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nOdegaard \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Real Madrid \u0111\u1ea9y t\u1edbi CLB Heerenveen c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 Lan theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 1 n\u0103m. Trong th\u1eddi gian cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n t\u1ea1i Heerenveen, sao tr\u1ebb 19 tu\u1ed5i ra s\u00e2n t\u1edbi 38 l\u1ea7n v\u00e0 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng gi\u00fap anh tr\u1ee5 l\u1ea1i \u1edf Bernabeu.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Julen Lopetegui kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Odegaard, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 19 tu\u1ed5i ra \u0111i theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Anh mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Odegaard</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Anh bao g\u1ed3m Middlebrough, Aston Villa v\u00e0 Derby County mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Martin Odegaard r\u1eddi Real Madrid \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Anh mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Martin Odegaard r\u1eddi Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Anh mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Martin Odegaard r\u1eddi Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/3-doi-bong-anh-muon-co-than-dong-cua-real-madrid.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Odegaard s\u1eafp t\u1edbi Anh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng CLB \u1edf n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 19 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n, qua \u0111\u00f3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh. Nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Real s\u1ebd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf x\u1ee9 s\u1edf s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u1edf ch\u1ed7 b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Na Uy c\u00f3 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ebfn Anh ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng hay kh\u00f4ng. Hi\u1ec7n Odegaard \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb v\u00e0 Real mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ec3 anh t\u1ef1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5448","checkdouble":"194418"},{"date":"00:33 14/08","title":"Sau Iniesta v\u00e0 Pique, th\u00eam m\u1ed9t tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C chia tay \u0110T TBN","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/5/sau-iniesta-va-pique-them-mot-tru-cot-chinh-thuc-chia-tay-dt-tbn.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>David Silva chia tay \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha, sau Andres Iniesta v\u00e0 Gerard Pique th\u00ec ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Man City l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean ti\u1ebfp theo chia tay La Roja.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">David Silva tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 chia tay \u0110T TBN</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y \u00edt gi\u1edd, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 David Silva chia tay \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha. Ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Man xanh \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chia tay La Roja sau 12 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1986 mu\u1ed1n t\u1eadp trung thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho Man City, c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 quan t\u00e2m nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ebfn gia \u0111\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"David Silva chia tay \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"David Silva chia tay \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/29/David-Silva-chia-tay-DT-Tay-Ban-Nha-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>&nbsp;David Silva chia tay \u0110T TBN</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nDavid Silva ch\u01a1i cho \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha t\u1eeb n\u0103m 2006, t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn nay anh gi\u00e0nh 3 danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn, bao g\u1ed3m 2 ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Euro v\u00e0o c\u00e1c n\u0103m 2008 v\u00e0 2012 c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t danh hi\u1ec7u v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2010.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 32 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f3 125 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00e0 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 35 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ed1t. 3 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 World Cup 2014, Euro 2016 v\u00e0 World Cup 2018&nbsp;\u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 s\u1edf B\u00f2 t\u00f3t \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng ti\u1ebfn qu\u00e1 s\u00e2u.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede World Cup 2018, T\u00e2y Ban Nha d\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 tr\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga. L\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i &quot;tiki-taka&quot; \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u tho\u00e1i tr\u00e0o, David Silva mu\u1ed1n nh\u01b0\u1eddng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed cho nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean tr\u1ebb h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau Andres Iniesta v\u00e0 Gerard Pique, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 32 tu\u1ed5i l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean th\u1ee9 3 chia tay \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>David Silva vi\u1ebft t\u00e2m th\u01b0 chia tay \u0110TQG</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh chia tay \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 david Silva \u0111\u00e3 vi\u1ebft m\u1ed9t b\u1ee9c th\u01b0 chia tay \u0111\u1ea7y x\u00fac \u0111\u1ed9ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"David Silva\" title=\"David Silva\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/5/162516-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>David Silva vi\u1ebft t\u00e2m th\u01b0 chia tay \u0110T TBN</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 suy ngh\u0129 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh chia tay \u0110T TBN, \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n nh\u1ea5t trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i. \u0110TQG \u0111\u00e3 cho t\u00f4i m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9, t\u00f4i t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o khi c\u00f3 12 n\u0103m v\u00e0 125 tr\u1eadn trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T TBN&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u1ea3 World Cup v\u00e0 Euro c\u00f9ng \u0110TQG, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng n\u0103m th\u00e1ng t\u01b0\u01a1i \u0111\u1eb9p nh\u1ea5t trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i. C\u1ea3m \u01a1n NHM, L\u0110B\u0110 TBN, c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c HLV, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap t\u00f4i c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng k\u00fd \u1ee9c \u0111\u1eb9p trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110TQG&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&quot;T\u00f4i c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u1ea3m \u01a1n gia \u0111\u00ecnh t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 t\u00f4i trong bao n\u0103m qua, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 h\u1ecd t\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay. Ch\u00fac \u0110T TBN s\u1ebd th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, t\u00f4i tin \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n s\u1ebd v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua nh\u1eefng kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn danh hi\u1ec7u v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch \u1edf nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5447","checkdouble":"194420"},{"date":"22:56 13/08","title":"Alan Shearer: \u201cT\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean n\u1ebfu Pogba t\u1edbi Barca\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/10/alan-shearer-toi-se-khong-ngac-nhien-neu-pogba-toi-barca.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Alan Shearer ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Paul Pogba, c\u1ef1u sao tuy\u1ec3n Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd n\u1ebfu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p r\u1eddi M.U t\u1edbi Barca trong th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 CN H\u00e8 2018.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Barca r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Pogba</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAndres Iniesta \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eddi Barca sau g\u1ea7n 20 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalan \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Arthur v\u00e0 Arturo Vidal song HLV Ernesto Valverde v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi TBN mu\u1ed1n Barca mua th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m \u1edf \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p cao.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alan Shearer ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Paul Pogba h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Alan Shearer ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Paul Pogba h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/Alan-Shearer-phat-bieu-ve-Paul-Pogba-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Barca r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Paul Pogba</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/chu-tich-barca-chua-tu-bo-y-dinh-cuom-pogba-khoi-mu-184-194382.html\" target=\"_blank\">Barca mu\u1ed1n mua Pogba</span>, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eafm ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a M.U nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa. Theo Don Balon, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalan \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eed ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u00ed m\u1eadt \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i sao 25 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Pogba r\u1eddi Old Trafford, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993 y\u00eau c\u1ea7u, ngo\u00e0i ra h\u1ecd c\u00f2n s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng cho anh m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1ec1 ph\u00eda M.U, Barca d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh chi t\u1edbi 130 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng ti\u1ec1n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng. H\u1ecd \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 H\u00e8 2018 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Alan Shearer n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Barca chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Pogba</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Alan Shearer ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Paul Pogba, c\u1ef1u sao tuy\u1ec3n Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd n\u1ebfu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p r\u1eddi M.U t\u1edbi Barca trong th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 CN H\u00e8 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Day khong phai lan dau tien Mino Raiola giat day de Paul Pogba doi roi Man Utd.\" title=\"\u0110\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean Mino Raiola gi\u1eadt d\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec3 Paul Pogba \u0111\u00f2i r\u1eddi Man Utd.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/10/barca-van-nuoi-hy-vong-so-huu-pogba.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Alan Shearer n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Pogba t\u1edbi Barca</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ecdc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin cho th\u1ea5y Barca mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Pogba, n\u1ebfu c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Camp Nou v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i th\u00e1ng 8 t\u00f4i c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean. Ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn Pogba th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi \u1edf World Cup 2018, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 kh\u1ee7ng khi\u1ebfp d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a Didier Deschamps\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cPogba ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ee9ng minh t\u1ea7m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o M.U, nh\u01b0ng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o Mourinho. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u1ec9 ph\u00e1t huy nh\u1eefng g\u00ec l\u00e0 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t n\u1ebfu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7t v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t b\u1ec7 ph\u00f3ng h\u1ee3p l\u00fd, c\u00f2n kh\u00f4ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm m\u1ed9t b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 h\u1ee3p l\u00fd h\u01a1n\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cN\u1ebfu Pogba mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi M.U c\u00f2n Barca thi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn, t\u00f4i tin c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Camp Nou trong th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 CN H\u00e8 2018\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5446","checkdouble":"194416"},{"date":"22:56 13/08","title":"\"Bom x\u1ecbt\" Chelsea k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi AC Milan trong v\u00e0i gi\u1edd t\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/13/bom-xit-chelsea-ky-hop-dong-voi-ac-milan-trong-vai-gio-toi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Tiemoue Bakayoko t\u1edbi AC Milan \u0111ang r\u1ea5t cao, theo Goal c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u01a1i Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf Italia \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Milan.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">AC Milan \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua Bakayoko</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTiemoue Bakayoko \u0111ang g\u1eb7p \u00e1p l\u1ef1c c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn \u1edf Chelsea, v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c HLV Sarri s\u1edf h\u1eefu Kante, Jorginho, Fabregas, Barkley, Drinkwater v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 t\u00e2n binh Kovacic n\u1eefa, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a Bakayoko \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tiemoue Bakayoko t\u1edbi AC Milan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tiemoue Bakayoko t\u1edbi AC Milan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/20/Tiemoue-Bakayoko-toi-AC-Milan-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Tiemoue Bakayoko \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c AC Milan quan t\u00e2m</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u1edf Chelsea, AC Milan \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1994. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Milan \u0111ang r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ef1u sao Monaco.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/them-mot-cau-thu-sap-roi-chelsea-172-194238.html\" target=\"_blank\">Tiemoue Bakayoko t\u1edbi AC Milan</span> \u0111ang r\u1ea5t cao, theo Goal c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u01a1i Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf Italia \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Milan.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, AC Milan s\u1ebd m\u01b0\u1ee3n Bakayoko m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed 5 tri\u1ec7u euro, sau \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd mua \u0111\u1ee9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19 v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed 35 tri\u1ec7u euro. Nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 AC Milan b\u1ecf ra t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 40 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Bakayoko s\u1eafp ra m\u1eaft AC Milan</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Tiemoue Bakayoko t\u1edbi AC Milan \u0111ang r\u1ea5t cao, theo Goal c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u01a1i Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf Italia \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Milan.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tiemoue Bakayoko t\u1edbi AC Milan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Tiemoue Bakayoko t\u1edbi AC Milan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/9/Tiemoue-Bakayoko-toi-AC-Milan-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Bakayoko s\u1eafp k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi AC Milan</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nBakayoko \u0111\u00e3 bay t\u1edbi Milan v\u00e0o h\u00f4m qua, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 Milan. Anh \u0111ang di chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea1i b\u1ea3n doanh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Milan \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n San Siro.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Bakayoko t\u1edbi AC Milan s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 trong v\u00e0i gi\u1edd t\u1edbi. D\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng \u1edf Chelsea nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1994 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf s\u00e2n San Siro.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho AC Milan, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 v\u1edbi Chelsea \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 b\u1edfi trong tay HLV Sarri \u0111ang c\u00f3 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5445","checkdouble":"194417"},{"date":"23:40 13/08","title":"\u0110\u00e2y! C\u00e1i t\u00ean ti\u1ebfp theo r\u1eddi Liverpool \u1edf H\u00e8 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/1/24/day-cai-ten-tiep-theo-roi-liverpool-o-he-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Liverpool b\u00e1n Ragnar Klavan l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra trong th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 CN H\u00e8 2018, s\u1ef1 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a Nat Phillips cho ph\u00e9p c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 32 tu\u1ed5i r\u1eddi Anfield.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Klopp t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n Klavan cho Newcastle</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua Ragnar Klavan kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Liverpool, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1986 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea1nh tranh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh, khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i anh c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Liverpool b\u00e1n Ragnar Klavan \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Liverpool b\u00e1n Ragnar Klavan \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/Liverpool-ban-Ragnar-Klavan-o-He-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Klopp t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n Klavan cho Newcastle</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0i gi\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 H\u00e8 2018 \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh ch\u1eb7n chi\u1ec1u mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, Newcastle \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ecfi mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 32 tu\u1ed5i, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 6 tri\u1ec7u euro mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1986, song HLV Klopp \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c Matip v\u00e0 Lovren d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn HLV Klopp kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 Ragnar Klavan ra \u0111i, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u1eef c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 32 tu\u1ed5i \u1edf l\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1c. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Ragnar Klavan \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u01a1n. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1986 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc West Ham \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Klopp s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Van Dijk v\u00e0 Gomez \u1edf trung t\u00e2m h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7, vi\u1ec7c Matip v\u00e0 Lovren s\u1eafp tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb d\u00e0i d\u00e0i. Klavan \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Liverpool s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n Klavan</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Liverpool b\u00e1n Ragnar Klavan l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra trong th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 CN H\u00e8 2018, s\u1ef1 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a Nat Phillips cho ph\u00e9p c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 32 tu\u1ed5i r\u1eddi Anfield.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Klavan vs Aguero\" title=\"Klavan vs Aguero\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/3/19/Thong-tin-luc-luong-tran-Brighton-vs-Liverpool-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Klavan s\u1eafp r\u1eddi Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, sao tr\u1ebb Nat Phillips \u0111\u00e3 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u, HLV Klopp s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 Klavan ra \u0111i, qua \u0111\u00f3 t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 21 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 Italia mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 32 tu\u1ed5i, Liverpool s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh ra \u0111i n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 5 tri\u1ec7u euro.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i Klavan th\u00ec Divock Origi v\u00e0 Sheyi Ojo c\u0169ng \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch r\u1eddi Anfield, b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i n\u00e0y c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Liverpool \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5444","checkdouble":"194419"},{"date":"06:05 14/08","title":"X\u1eed l\u00fd ng\u1edb ng\u1ea9n, Petr Cech tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh tr\u00f2 c\u01b0\u1eddi tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/xu-ly-ngo-ngan-petr-cech-tro-thanh-tro-cuoi-tren-mang-xa-hoi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Petr Cech b\u1ecb Leverkusen tr\u00eau t\u1ee9c tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i. Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t pha x\u1eed l\u00fd ng\u1edb ng\u1ea9n c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n k\u1ef3 c\u1ef1u n\u00e0y. Ch\u00ednh Cech sau \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng c\u00f3 ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng r\u1ea5t g\u1eaft.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Cech g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, Arsenal b\u1ecf ra s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 25 tri\u1ec7u Euro chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Bernd Leno v\u1ec1 t\u1eeb Leverkusen. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1 Premier League 2018/19, HLV Unai Emery quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n k\u1ef3 c\u1ef1u Petr Cech b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nK\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec kh\u1ea3 quan. Arsenal th\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 0-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Emirates v\u00e0 Cech c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng bi\u1ec3u hi\u1ec7n r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng. HLV Emery ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1o c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng ngay ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 song th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi CH S\u00e9c l\u1ea1i lu\u00f4n g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 \u1edf nh\u1eefng pha chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Petr Cech b\u1ecb Leverkusen tr\u00eau t\u1ee9c tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Petr Cech b\u1ecb Leverkusen tr\u00eau t\u1ee9c tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/14/xu-ly-ngo-ngan-petr-cech-tro-thanh-tro-cuoi-tren-mang-xa-hoi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Petr Cech b\u1ecb Leverkusen tr\u00eau t\u1ee9c tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110i\u1ec3n h\u00ecnh l\u00e0 sau khi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n v\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a Matteo Guendouzi, Cech thay v\u00ec \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng cho h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i Hector Bellerin \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1 th\u1eb3ng v\u1ec1 c\u1ea7u m\u00f4n, b\u00f3ng \u0111i s\u1ea1t c\u1ed9t d\u1ecdc, su\u00fdt t\u1ea1o n\u00ean b\u00e0n thua.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>M\u00e0n c\u00e3i v\u00e3 v\u1edbi Leverkusen</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n Twitter ti\u1ebfng Anh c\u1ee7a Leverkusen \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u0103ng m\u1ed9t video ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea1o n\u00ean b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Bernd Leno, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ng\u1ed3i tr\u00ean gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City. Sau \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd ch\u00fa th\u00edch b\u00ean d\u01b0\u1edbi: \u201cNh\u00ecn v\u00e0o tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p n\u00e0y, b\u1ea1n t\u1ef1 h\u1ecfi c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u1edf s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o?\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cech\" title=\"Cech\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/HLV-Unai-Emery-noi-ve-Arsenal-sau-tran-thua-Man-City-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Arsenal \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, Cech l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng nh\u00ecn s\u1ef1 vi\u1ec7c d\u01b0\u1edbi g\u00f3c \u0111\u1ed9 h\u00e0i h\u01b0\u1edbc. Petr Cech b\u1ecb Leverkusen tr\u00eau t\u1ee9c tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i v\u00e0 d\u00f9ng ch\u00ednh Twitter ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3: \u201c\u1ede Arsenal, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i chia s\u1ebb nh\u1eefng gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb quan tr\u1ecdng khi\u1ebfn ch\u00fang t\u00f4i tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t CLB l\u1edbn, kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u1edf kh\u00eda c\u1ea1nh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1\u201d, anh vi\u1ebft.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cC\u1ea1nh tranh c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng, s\u1ef1 chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p v\u00e0 tinh th\u1ea7n th\u1ec3 thao l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea1n d\u1ea1y cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb. Th\u1eadt \u0111\u00e1ng bu\u1ed3n khi c\u00e1c CLB kh\u00e1c kh\u00f4ng chia s\u1ebb c\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau khi b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u00edch danh,\u00a0 Leverkusen \u0111\u00e3 l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0a ra m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi xin l\u1ed7i: \u201cCh\u00e0o Petr. C\u00f3 v\u1ebb nh\u01b0 tr\u00f2 \u0111\u00f9a c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c mu\u1ed1n g\u1eb7p Leno, c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb r\u1ebd sang m\u1ed9t chi\u1ec1u h\u01b0\u1edbng kh\u1eafc nghi\u1ec7t, c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n h\u01a1n d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh\u201d, Leverkusen \u0111\u0103ng tr\u00ean Twitter.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat \u0111\u00f9a gi\u1ee1n th\u00f4i. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i chia s\u1ebb t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i v\u00e0 ch\u00fac b\u1ea1n c\u00f9ng CLB l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p nh\u1ea5t. Pha c\u1ee9u thua 1 vs 1 v\u1edbi Aguero l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t tuy\u1ec7t!\u201d<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Arsenal tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/du-am-arsenal-02-man-city-sterling-va-cau-tra-loi-cho-ca-nuoc-anh-172-194405.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m Arsenal 0-2 Man City: Sterling v\u00e0 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi cho c\u1ea3 n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/5-diem-nhan-sau-chien-thang-thuyet-phuc-cua-man-city-truoc-arsenal-172-194359.html\">5 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a Man City tr\u01b0\u1edbc Arsenal</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-02-man-city-pep-team-khong-ngu-quen-tren-chien-thang-172-194353.html\">Arsenal 0-2 Man City: \u201cPep Team\u201d kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ee7 qu\u00ean tr\u00ean chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-emery-toi-muon-cac-cau-thu-arsenal-co-trach-nhiem-hon-172-194391.html\">HLV Emery: T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Arsenal c\u00f3 tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m h\u01a1n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/pep-noi-gi-ve-chien-thang-truoc-arsenal-172-194368.html\">Pep n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Arsenal?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5443","checkdouble":"194421"},{"date":"06:54 14/08","title":"H\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 m\u00e1ch Emery c\u00e1ch \u0111\u01b0a Arsenal t\u00ecm l\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/5/3/hoc-tro-mach-emery-cach-dua-arsenal-tim-lai-chien-thang.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Pierre-Emerick Aubameyang ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Alexandre Lacazette. Anh tin r\u1eb1ng HLV Unai Emery ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed c\u1ea3 hai trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t c\u1ee7a Arsenal.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Aubameyang l\u00e0m lu m\u1edd Lacazette</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAlexandre Lacazette gia nh\u1eadp Arsenal \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a 2017/18 t\u1eeb Lyon v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 l\u00ean t\u1edbi 47 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Sau m\u1ed9t qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ea7u g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, d\u1ea7n d\u00e0 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 sa s\u00fat phong \u0111\u1ed9. T\u1eeb th\u00e1ng 11 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i cho t\u1edbi th\u00e1ng 4 n\u0103m nay, anh ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 4 b\u00e0n t\u1ea1i Premier League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nS\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Pierre-Emerick Aubameyang t\u1eeb Dortmund \u0111\u00e3 mang t\u1edbi l\u00e0n gi\u00f3 m\u1edbi cho Arsenal. 13 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u1eeda cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Gabon ghi t\u1edbi 10 b\u00e0n cho h\u1ecd.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pierre-Emerick Aubameyang ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Alexandre Lacazette h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Pierre-Emerick Aubameyang ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Alexandre Lacazette h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/3/Truoc-tran-Atletico-vs-Arsenal-Thap-sang-niem-hy-vong-tu-Lacazette-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Aubameyang ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Alexandre Lacazette</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ea3 hai c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 song h\u00e0nh</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAubameyang \u0111\u00e1 cao nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng Arsenal khi h\u1ecd ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Man City t\u1edbi s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 \u1edf v\u00f2ng m\u1edf m\u00e0n Premier League. Nh\u01b0ng Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 ch\u1ec9 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t khi Lacazette \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tung v\u00e0o s\u00e2n v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i 29 tu\u1ed5i tin r\u1eb1ng h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i v\u1edbi nhau th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n theo h\u01b0\u1edbng l\u1ea1c quan\u201d, Pierre-Emerick Aubameyang ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Alexandre Lacazette tr\u00ean ESPN. \u201cC\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 li\u00ean k\u1ebft gi\u1eefa ch\u00fang t\u00f4i khi c\u1ea3 hai c\u00f9ng \u1edf tr\u00ean s\u00e2n. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm nhau v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 li\u00ean h\u1ec7 nh\u01b0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Man City v\u1eeba qua.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i d\u1ea1t tr\u00e1i n\u1ebfu Lacazette \u1edf trung t\u00e2m. C\u1ea3 hai ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c v\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\nArsenal \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ee9ng ch\u1ecbu nhi\u1ec1u l\u1eddi ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch sau tr\u1eadn thua 0-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Aubameyang ki\u00ean quy\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng c\u00f2n qu\u00e1 s\u1edbm \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 v\u1ec1 Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Unai Emery. \u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 th\u00edch nghi v\u1edbi HLV m\u1edbi v\u00e0 t\u00edch h\u1ee3p nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi\u201d, c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Dortmund n\u00f3i th\u00eam.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cTh\u1eadt kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean khi Man City r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c, ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 d\u1ea7n ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n sau tr\u01b0\u1edbc Chelsea. Th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a HLV m\u1edbi l\u00e0 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ea5t, gia t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ed9 pressing v\u00e0 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m cao. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 phong c\u00e1ch ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Arsenal tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-emery-toi-muon-cac-cau-thu-arsenal-co-trach-nhiem-hon-172-194391.html\">HLV Emery: T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Arsenal c\u00f3 tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m h\u01a1n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/thierry-henry-sap-tro-lai-anh-doi-dau-arsenal-172-194380.html\">Thierry Henry s\u1eafp tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Anh \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Arsenal</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-emery-noi-gi-ve-quyet-dinh-su-dung-cech-va-loai-bo-leno-172-194371.html\">HLV Emery n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Cech v\u00e0 lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf Leno?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/pep-noi-gi-ve-chien-thang-truoc-arsenal-172-194368.html\">Pep n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Arsenal?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/5-diem-nhan-sau-chien-thang-thuyet-phuc-cua-man-city-truoc-arsenal-172-194359.html\">5 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a Man City tr\u01b0\u1edbc Arsenal</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5442","checkdouble":"194423"},{"date":"15:44 13/08","title":"\"Ronaldo b\u00e9o\" nh\u1eadp vi\u1ec7n khi \u0111i ngh\u1ec9 \u1edf T\u00e2y Ban Nha","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/13/ronaldo-beo-nhap-vien-khi-di-nghi-o-tay-ban-nha.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2> Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Brazil \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb \u1edf Ibiza, v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p xu\u1ea5t vi\u1ec7n v\u00e0o 13/8.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">Ronaldo \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7n t\u1ed1i 10/8 khi \u0111ang trong k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 v\u1edbi b\u1ea1n g\u00e1i Celina Locks. Chi\u1ec1u 12/8, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o hai l\u1ea7n \u0111o\u1ea1t Qu\u1ea3 B\u00f3ng V\u00e0ng tr\u1ea5n an d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn khi th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o l\u00ean Twitter: \"T\u00f4i v\u1eeba nh\u1eadp vi\u1ec7n v\u00ec nhi\u1ec5m virus c\u00fam \u1edf Ibiza, nh\u01b0ng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t. Ng\u00e0y mai t\u00f4i s\u1ebd xu\u1ea5t vi\u1ec7n v\u00e0 v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0. C\u1ea3m \u01a1n s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n\".<br />\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ronaldo b\u00e9o nh\u1eadp vi\u1ec7n khi \u0111i ngh\u1ec9 \u1edf T\u00e2y Ban Nha  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ronaldo b\u00e9o nh\u1eadp vi\u1ec7n khi \u0111i ngh\u1ec9 \u1edf T\u00e2y Ban Nha  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/ronaldo-1383-1534091941.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ronaldo v\u00e0 b\u1ea1n g\u00e1i Celina trong k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 \u1edf Ibiza. \u1ea2nh: Backgrid.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\nAnh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean t\u1edbi h\u00f2n \u0111\u1ea3o du l\u1ecbch n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng \u1edf T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00e0 th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u0169ng s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y. Danh th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 b\u1ea1n g\u00e1i \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e2y du l\u1ecbch t\u1eeb th\u00e1ng 7 v\u00e0 thu\u00ea du thuy\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec3 th\u01b0\u1edfng ngo\u1ea1n c\u1ea3nh \u0111\u1eb9p. H\u1ecd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u h\u1eb9n h\u00f2 k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m 2015.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nTh\u00e1ng 1/2012, danh th\u1ee7 41 tu\u1ed5i t\u1eebng b\u1ecb s\u1ed1t xu\u1ea5t huy\u1ebft Dengue. Khi \u0111\u00f3 anh c\u0169ng ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 s\u1ef1 vi\u1ec7c tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nVua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi World Cup 2002 t\u1eebng b\u1ecb ch\u1ea9n \u0111o\u00e1n b\u1ec7nh li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn gi\u00e1p, khi\u1ebfn anh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n khi thi \u0111\u1ea5u. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1edbi s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a Ronaldo. </div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5441","checkdouble":"194394"}]}